paper_metadata.title: Desire for contraceptive counseling among women seeking first-trimester abortion

study_characteristics.outcomes_evidence_citation: We asked women about whether they wanted to discuss contraception, specific topics they wanted to discuss, reasons why they may not want contraceptive counseling and whether they wanted to receive contraceptive services as part of their abortion care
study_characteristics.design_evidence_citation: We conducted a cross-sectional study by distributing self-administered anonymous surveys

evidence_citations.country_citation: We conducted a cross-sectional study by distributing self-administered anonymous surveys to women seeking first-trimester medical or surgical abortion at three clinics in Sacramento, Chicago and Cleveland
evidence_citations.target_population_citation: We conducted a cross-sectional study by distributing self-administered anonymous surveys to women seeking first-trimester medical or surgical abortion
